_sText:
A fun map for up to 34 players. The crates are breakable and some has a grenade on top of them. The doors in the "Underground" under the map opens automatically when you step close to them.

------ADDED IN V2------

 -Barrels and more crates
 -Glass on the Deagle platform
 -Fixed some lightning
 -One more secret place
 -My own ladders and rails
 -A spinning sign in the "Underground"
 -A hidden weapon
